    <item>
      <title>中东危机中油价上涨，亚洲股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/asian-stocks-tumble-as-oil-jumps-amid-mideast-woes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东紧张局势升级的新担忧和忧虑，亚洲股市暴跌，而石油价格飙升。据两名美国官员称，在德黑兰发动火箭和无人机袭击后不到一周，以色列对伊朗发动了导弹袭击，避险资产正在上涨。艾薇儿·洪 (Avril Hong) 接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/asian-stocks-tumble-as-oil-jumps-amid-mideast-woes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 03:37:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳新银行正在与澳大利亚养老金部门就印度投资进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/anz-bank-in-talks-with-australia-pensions-on-india-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位银行高级官员表示，澳新银行集团控股有限公司正在与澳大利亚养老基金就投资印度基础设施资产及其债务市场进行讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/anz-bank-in-talks-with-australia-pensions-on-india-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 03:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东问题、鹰派美联储情绪低迷，亚洲股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/asian-stocks-slump-as-mideast-woes-hawkish-fed-sour-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东紧张局势升级的担忧以及对美国利率长期走高的担忧，市场普遍出现避险情绪，亚洲股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/asian-stocks-slump-as-mideast-woes-hawkish-fed-sour-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东风险引发避险情绪，国债反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/treasuries-jump-with-dollar-as-middle-east-risks-fan-haven-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东冲突升级的担忧提振了对避险资产的需求，美国国债随美元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/treasuries-jump-with-dollar-as-middle-east-risks-fan-haven-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 01:39:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势影响市场，金价随金属价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/gold-xauusd-set-for-fifth-weekly-gain-on-increasing-mideast-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东冲突的担忧加剧，促使投资者转向传统的避险资产，金价飙升至接近新纪录高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/gold-xauusd-set-for-fifth-weekly-gain-on-increasing-mideast-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 00:59:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称以色列袭击伊朗目标后油价跃升至 90 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员称以色列袭击了伊朗目标后，油价上涨，布伦特原油价格上涨，原因是担心可能爆发更广泛的地区冲突，从而危及原油供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:23:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔与穆迪一起下调以色列的地缘政治风险评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/s-p-downgrades-israel-rating-on-heightened-geopolitical-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中东地缘政治风险升级，标准普尔全球评级与穆迪评级一起下调了以色列的主权信用评分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/s-p-downgrades-israel-rating-on-heightened-geopolitical-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:56:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突导致股市暴跌，避险资产飙升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球市场受到中东新冲突的冲击，导致股市走低，而石油和包括国债和美元在内的避险资产则上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
